"{\n  \"text\": \"Hey everybody, I just want to make a quick uh video about autoimmune disorders. Your gut is in charge of your bodily functions and in particular your immune system, which is your body's maintenance. And when your body's maintenance is going haywire, it's called an autoimmune disorder. It's basically your body is confusing sickness with health. So a good example is an allergy where you get cold-like symptoms because you inhaled some sort of pollen. It's not because you're actually sick, it's because the body is confused in thinking that the pollen is actually a sickness. Now, this is not a problem with a healthy gut. A healthy, diverse gut bacteria and a web of life that lives in the gut isn't going to be confused by this. It's when the gut becomes alienated from the body that it starts to attack the body in ways that aren't beneficial. It starts to heal healthy tissue. This is a huge problem in America. We have autoimmune disorders coming out of the kazoo, and most of us are suffering from them. You can fix the gut, you can fix the autoimmune disorders. Anyway, thanks, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hey everybody, I just want to make a quick uh video about autoimmune disorders.\",\n      \"start\": 0.24,\n      \"end\": 4.56,\n      \"duration\": 4.32,\n      \"confidence\": 0.992,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" He\",\n          \"start\": 0.24,\n          \"end\": 0.4,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 0.996\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"y\",\n          \"start\": 0.4,\n          \"end\": 0.48,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 0.56,\n          \"end\": 0.72,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 0.72,\n          \"end\": 0.88,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\